## Encoding decisions and deviations

1. **Lemmas 8.4/8.5 are proved, in multiplied-out integer form.**  (125) is stated as
   `|D| В· #{o = 0} = ОЈ_О» (2 m_О» вҲ’ |X|)` over `в„Ө` (no division), with `D` the `рқ”ҪвӮӮ`-linear
